"PG.pl",
"PGbasicmacros.pl",
"PGchoicemacros.pl",
"PGanswermacros.pl",
"PGauxiliaryFunctions.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(2,20,1);
$b = random(2,20,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));

Suppose that \( f(x) = $a x^{e} + $b e^{x} \).  Find \(f'(2)\).

$BR $BR

\(f'(2)\) = \{ans_rule(30) \}
$BR

EOT

$ans = ($a*exp(1))*2**(exp(1)-1) + ($b)*exp(2) ;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

ENDDOCUMENT();


